  "description_html": "<p><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"29\">IIITDM-K&rsquo;s Flagship Fest:</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"33\" data-end=\"669\" data-is-only-node=\"\" data-is-last-node=\"\">\n<li data-start=\"33\" data-end=\"106\">Welcome to IIITDM-K&rsquo;s Flagship fest organised by Quriosity Quiz Club.</li>\n<li data-start=\"108\" data-end=\"204\">The quiz consists of a prelims round and a finals round where top 6 teams make it to finals.</li>\n<li data-start=\"206\" data-end=\"413\">Quiz topics are wide and varied ranging from sports, history, culture, contemporary, literature etc... with many finding inspiration from the theme &ldquo;Chrono-sync- a moment where the future meets the past&rdquo;</li>\n<li data-start=\"415\" data-end=\"580\">Connections ought to be made as most questions involve well known things, phenomenon and events with just additional twists in the question to put you off track.</li>\n<li data-start=\"582\" data-end=\"669\" data-is-last-node=\"\">Quiz organisers will have all final say in decisions and will be binding on the spot.</li>\n</ul>",
